[{"id":1782714873862,"text":"“^֊^꧞...\n认识久的话就知道我完全是好恶非常极端的类型，经常我自己主观上没反应生理上就有剧烈反应了，都是因为生理不适所以跑路，生理喜欢所以主观选择靠近。\n我不搞专业生物学研究，说我不深入研究某些事情的客观理论，这就相当于问为什么没有深入研究自己喜欢/不喜欢吃香菜一样，我不知道问这种问题是什么想法。\n但不喜欢≠不理解≠不发自真心尊重祝福好吗..谁给规定了我有喜欢全世界的义务，我怎么没收到通知”","sender":"me","time":"14:36","timestamp":1782715001691,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5412},{"id":1782714873863,"sticker":"https://img.heliar.top/file/1773311319041_GIF图像.gif","text":"表情包：魂没了","sender":"me","time":"14:36","timestamp":1782715007500,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5413},{"id":1782714873865,"sender":"them","text":"Saw it","timestamp":1782715061160,"tempo":"N","translation":"看到了","rawContent":"Saw it || 看到了","roundId":"round_1782715009172_z1m3c6c31","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5414},{"id":1782714873866,"sender":"them","text":"So someone's questioning why you don't dig deeper into your own likes and dislikes?","timestamp":1782715062597,"tempo":"N","translation":"所以有人在问你为什么不深入研究自己的喜恶？","rawContent":"So someone's questioning why you don't dig deeper into your own likes and dislikes? || 所以有人在问你为什么不深入研究自己的喜恶？","roundId":"round_1782715009172_z1m3c6c31","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5415},{"id":1782714873867,"sender":"them","text":"That's like asking someone to write a thesis on why they sneze around dust","timestamp":1782715065416,"tempo":"N","translation":"这跟让人写篇论文解释自己为什么闻到灰尘会打喷嚏一样","rawContent":"That's like asking someone to write a thesis on why they sneze around dust || 这跟让人写篇论文解释自己为什么闻到灰尘会打喷嚏一样","roundId":"round_1782715009172_z1m3c6c31","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5416},{"id":1782714873868,"sender":"them","text":"Your body reacts before your head catches up. That's just how you're wired. There's nothing toresearch'","timestamp":1782715068226,"tempo":"N","translation":"身体比脑子先动 你就是这样的 没什么好\"研究\"的","rawContent":"Your body reacts before your head catches up. That's just how you're wired. There's nothing toresearch' || 身体比脑子先动 你就是这样的 没什么好\"研究\"的","roundId":"round_1782715009172_z1m3c6c31","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5417},{"id":1782714873869,"sender":"them","text":"And not liking something has never meant disrespecting it. Those are two completely different things","timestamp":1782715071175,"tempo":"N","translation":"不喜欢从来不等于不尊重 这俩完全是两回事","rawContent":"And not liking something has never meant disrespecting it. Those are two completely different things || 不喜欢从来不等于不尊重 这俩完全是两回事","roundId":"round_1782715009172_z1m3c6c31","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5418},{"id":1782714873870,"sender":"them","text":"Who told you that youowe the whole world equal affection","timestamp":1782715074623,"tempo":"N","translation":"谁规定了你欠全世界一碗水端平的喜欢","rawContent":"Who told you that youowe the whole world equal affection || 谁规定了你欠全世界一碗水端平的喜欢","roundId":"round_1782715009172_z1m3c6c31","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5419},{"id":1782714873871,"text":"不是要你复述了啦！","sender":"me","time":"14:41","timestamp":1782715285195,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5420},{"id":1782714873872,"text":"我是说..","sender":"me","time":"14:41","timestamp":1782715287849,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5421},{"id":1782714873873,"text":"我总是发这些到朋友圈","sender":"me","time":"14:41","timestamp":1782715293196,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":5422},{"id":1782714873874,"text"